caption: We booked an English version in the room 1987. However, everything was in French. Only the communication with Vincent was in English. The introduction, the guidance, the letters, the clues, etc,‚Ä¶ were in French. We were really frustrated and struggle. The staff said ‚Äúoh this is a new room so not everything is adapted to English‚Äù. Ok well so maybe try not to sell it then? Very disappointing from both the game to the staff.

Lots of fun trying out one of the escape games proposed here. Difficulty was advertised 2/5, be aware that it was fairly difficult and we received quite a bit of help from the host. Storyline and clues were well thought and hidden.

Tried the "black magic" game and loved it ! The atmosphere was creepy and the setting, simply amazing. We had a blast and Hafid, the game master, was really cool and made us have a great time. I'd happily come back and try another one !

We have done the military base 423. Even though advertised tgat an English version is available the guide wasn't really able to speak and the game had a few things which were not translated. Without my French friends I wouldn't have been able to solve the room. The room itself was alright. Definitely worth doing but not great. Just be aware that you need to be able to speak French (July 2018)
Love the rooms here ! I tried Alma 2.0 and the VR experience (must do from my point of view). Eclipse should not be done at less than 3, you'll miss fun interaction s and the ideal number IS FOUR !
the game I played was not too complex but they told me they had more challenging ones, so for the real players under us there is also options. Price/fun wise, it was good tho
Did the submarine game with a group, amazing experience, strongly advise to try it out. Will check out the other themes some day else.

The staff were very pleasant however I think we chose a "too easy" level. We finished 7 minutes early knowing that we were blocked for 20 minutes because the trunk had a technical problem despite the fact that we had the correct code. Disappointed that there is not an extra room for the Mayan temple.
An incredible experience, this place is worth recommending! I have excellent memories of my stay, marked by the quality of the welcome. I will happily return to explore the other rooms.

Good morning,  We were at Escap Lab last night with a jungle theme. The atmosphere was nice, but the Jungle Escape Room was too dark in our opinion. We came as beginners, and I find it a bit complicated to solve so many puzzles in the dark. Furthermore, for 28 euros per person (there were 7 of us), I found the room a little disappointing in terms of realism and dynamism.  There was too much written content and not enough intuitive steps. Coming from abroad, I had the opportunity to test other Escape Rooms in France, and I must say that the value for money here was really disappointing. Furthermore, the room was not big enough for a group of 7 people. We expected better, despite our beginner level.  I hope this comment can help you improve your visitors' experience in the future.
Today we played the ‚Äú1987‚Äù escape game with friends. Not a lot of digging but more reflection. Immersive room, quite difficult level. Overall very nice.
